  "commitMessage": "Apply Half-Split ratio to corner actions and snap areas (#1776)\n\n* Half size updates\n\n* Use half Ratio sizes in Corner Calculations\n\n* Add lock horizontal/vertical axis feature. Fix cyclic hotkeys hitting repeating the same state. Fix moving window flash after resize.\n\n* Prefer user-centric label over implementation.\n\n* Allow 1/2 size to be deselected from cyclic commands\n\n* Rename Half to Side. Affects  Shortcuts, Snap Areas, and General. Added migrations\n\n* Use legacy half names internally. Add aliases to create hooks for new side name to work for future progrmatic invocations.\n\n* Allow alias (leftSide for leftHalf, etc) to be used in the url api\n\n* Remove conflicting constraints for split % text input fields\n\n* A little more spacing for cycle sizes settings\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Daniel <daniel@trainoperator.co>\nCo-authored-by: Ryan Hanson <ryan@ryanhanson.dev>",
